=head1 NAME

PDL::GSLSF::COULOMB - PDL interface to GSL Special Functions

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This is an interface to the Special Function package present in the GNU Scientific Library. 

=head1 SYNOPSIS

=head1 Functions

